WEBVTT

00:03.100 --> 00:05.420
你到底在医务室里干什么?
What you're doing in the infirmary,

00:05.430 --> 00:06.790
那跟咱们做的有什么联系?
what's it gotta do with here?

00:06.800 --> 00:08.790
四天后的晚上  咱们就能离开这里了
Four days from now,on the night of the escape,

00:08.800 --> 00:11.720
我们有18分钟的 时间从医务室逃走
we'll have 18 minutes to get the bars off the window

00:11.730 --> 00:14.320
一共7个人将爬过电线
and for all seven of us to get across the wire

00:14.330 --> 00:15.120
越过高墙
and over the wall.

00:15.130 --> 00:17.720
-可能么?  -当然
-Is that doable?  -Of course.

00:17.730 --> 00:19.830
玛丽克鲁兹  是我 亲爱的  到底出了什么事?
Maricruz, what the hell is going on?

00:19.840 --> 00:23.290
赫克托说你可以慢慢享受牢狱生活
Yeah, well, Hector says you can serve your full sentence.

00:23.300 --> 00:24.680
你来这儿干嘛? 玛丽克鲁兹呢?
What are you doing here?where is Maricruz

00:24.690 --> 00:26.460
她再也不会来了
She's not gonna be coming around here any more.

00:26.470 --> 00:28.310
你在和我开玩笑?
It's ajoke, right?

00:28.320 --> 00:29.790
她现在跟我了
She's with me now.

00:29.800 --> 00:31.330
我只是想知道
I just need to know

00:31.340 --> 00:35.780
迈克尔·斯科菲尔德 为什么要为你换取绿卡?
what Michael Scofield wanted from you in exchange for the green card.

00:35.790 --> 00:38.560
在监狱里你要绿卡有什么用?
Why would you need a credit card in prison?

00:39.200 --> 00:42.720
如果我知道事情会 发展到现在这个地步的话
If I'd known how this was gonna turn out,

00:42.730 --> 00:44.300
我宁愿去捡联邦人员的烂摊子
I'd have gotten some crap job with the Feds.

00:44.310 --> 00:47.080
你再说下去我就把子弹放到你脑袋里
Keep talking like that,I'm gonna put a bullet in your head.

00:47.090 --> 00:48.690
我必须出去
I need to get out

00:48.700 --> 00:50.590
我还有我的生活
while I still got my life.

00:50.600 --> 00:51.550
爸爸! 爸爸!
Daddy! Daddy!

00:51.560 --> 00:52.780
事情变了
Things have changed.

00:52.790 --> 00:53.920
我想加入
I want in.

00:54.930 --> 00:56.020
怎么了?
So?

00:56.030 --> 00:57.820
咱们人太多了
We've got too many people.

00:57.830 --> 01:01.400
我算了一下  他们中必须有一个人放弃
I've done the math. One of 'em has to go.

01:02.960 --> 01:04.620
抱歉让您久等
Sorry to keep you waiting.

01:04.630 --> 01:06.690
没有关系
Oh, it's not a problem.

01:06.700 --> 01:09.590
很不错的简历
Impressive resume.

01:09.600 --> 01:11.970
多谢
Thank you.

01:11.980 --> 01:14.850
告诉我你为什么选择 继续在工程领域发展
Tell me why you chose to pursue a career in engineering.

01:14.860 --> 01:16.620
是这样的
Well, um...

01:16.630 --> 01:22.350
我一直对结构和几何学比较感兴趣
I've always been interested in structure.Geometry.

01:22.360 --> 01:25.750
(还有)物体是怎样结合在一起的
How things fit together.

01:25.760 --> 01:30.990
建筑物功能的展现...
How an object that performs a function

01:31.000 --> 01:32.390
同样也应该算作艺术
can also be a work of art.

01:32.400 --> 01:34.450
你的未来是怎么打算的?
What about the future?

01:34.460 --> 01:38.160
你认为5年后你会变成什么样?
Where do you see yourself in five years?

01:50.300 --> 01:53.830
一套制服  黑色
One suit, black.

03:36.130 --> 03:41.930
那个小男孩长大了么?
That baby boy all growed up yet?

03:42.560 --> 03:46.120
再过几年他就会闹的天翻地覆了
Oh, he's gonna raise hell the next few years.

03:46.130 --> 03:49.630
就像他妈妈那样
Take after his momma.

03:50.660 --> 03:55.600
是的  和过去差不多
Yeah, you know. Same old same up here.

03:56.600 --> 03:59.900
但是  嗯...
But, uh...

04:00.230 --> 04:02.950
情况有些不妙
things are getting pretty tense.

04:02.960 --> 04:05.620
比如冲突啊什么的
Like they're fixing to, uh... collide.

04:05.630 --> 04:08.250
了解我的意思么  吉米?
You know what I mean, Jimmy?

04:08.260 --> 04:13.190
可能会...
There's a potential situation.

04:13.200 --> 04:15.320
我找到进入医务室的办法了
I found our access to the infirmary.

04:15.330 --> 04:17.490
但我需要些时间来运作
I'm gonna need time to make it work.

04:17.500 --> 04:18.460
需要多久?
How much time?

04:18.470 --> 04:23.720
足够找出不用梯子就能从 20英尺深的排水管道里上去的方法
Enough for me to find my way up a 20 ft vertical drainpipe without using a ladder.

04:23.730 --> 04:25.720
明天的狱工我去不了了
I'll probably need to skip PI tomorrow

04:25.730 --> 04:27.520
如果我想把事情完成的话
if I wanna get this thing done.

04:27.530 --> 04:29.550
不能不去
You can't just skip it.

04:29.560 --> 04:30.890
这不像是上学
It ain't class.

04:30.900 --> 04:32.950
如果狱警突然来了怎么办?
What if one of the bulls decides to drop in?

04:32.960 --> 04:34.790
我已别无选择了  不是么?
I don't have a choice, do I?

04:34.800 --> 04:37.550
只要我们能打通警卫室的管道
Once we get through the pipe below the guards' room

04:37.560 --> 04:39.290
剩下的事就容易多了
it'll be easier.

04:39.300 --> 04:41.660
我不通过门就能到达各处
I can come and go without using the door,

04:41.670 --> 04:43.460
韦斯特莫兰德为咱们放哨
and with Westmoreland as lookout,

04:43.470 --> 04:45.690
还要再加个人来帮忙挖掘
we'll have one more man for digging.

04:45.700 --> 04:47.300
韦斯特莫兰德可不是省油的灯
He's a problem.

04:47.310 --> 04:49.840
咱们7个人要想爬过那墙根本不可能
All seven of us can't break over that wall in 18 minutes.

04:49.850 --> 04:51.930
你自己也说了  根本不可能
You said it yourself. It's impossible.

04:51.940 --> 04:55.450
兄弟我告诉你 咱们必须要甩掉一个人
Listen, man, one of us has gotta take a hike.

04:55.460 --> 04:56.940
我知道
I know.

04:56.950 --> 05:01.260
介意告诉我你们在谈什么么?
Mind if I share that with the rest of the class?

05:01.730 --> 05:05.810
很显然  大学生已经计算过
Apparently, college boy here did the math.

05:05.820 --> 05:09.180
我们的"车"已经超载了
Figured out that we got too many clowns in the car.

05:09.190 --> 05:10.330
也就是说虽然咱们都在这里挖洞
So one of us is in here digging,

05:10.330 --> 05:13.330
但最后却有个人连座位都落不着
but his seat ain't guaranteed.

05:13.340 --> 05:14.980
你有什么意见么  伙计?
How's this your problem?

05:14.990 --> 05:16.740
他根本就不知道自己在说什么
He doesn't know what he's talking about.

05:16.750 --> 05:18.870
要是不带我出去  我就不挖了
I won't dig if I'm not gonna go.

05:18.880 --> 05:20.870
我们必须决定不带谁
We need to decide who gets cut.

05:20.880 --> 05:25.850
这个大家心里早就有数了  对么?
I think we all can agree who that should be,right?

05:27.570 --> 05:31.260
噢  不好意思打扰你们了
Pardon me for interrupting,

05:31.270 --> 05:34.290
但是  呃...
but, uh...

05:34.780 --> 05:37.650
这像是什么?
what's that smell?

05:39.000 --> 05:43.560
我闻到了阴谋的气味
It smells a little like conspiracy.

05:43.570 --> 05:44.980
我们必须抓紧干活了
We need to get back to work.

05:44.990 --> 05:47.260
在此之前  我有话要说
I have an announcement to make.

05:47.270 --> 05:50.680
我发觉我越来越被你们忽视了
I've been growing leery of the way you all talk like I'm a lesser man,

05:50.690 --> 05:53.820
于是我就买了一份保单
so I bought an insurance policy.

05:53.830 --> 05:57.800
我和外面的兄弟通了电话 并把咱们的计划告诉了他
I called up my guy on the outside and I told him about our plan,

05:57.810 --> 06:01.180
我告诉他  如果可能 下周就能见到他了
and I told him in all likelihood I'll be seeing him next week.

06:01.190 --> 06:03.250
但是...
But...

06:03.530 --> 06:07.710
如果在逃走前5分钟或是成功后 20分钟还收不到我的消息的话
if he don't hear from me five minutes before the escape and 20 minutes after,

06:07.720 --> 06:12.620
他就会给监狱打电话 告诉他们全部的事情
I told him to call up the warden, blow the whistle on the whole thing.

06:12.630 --> 06:17.460
所以如果你们已经想好了如何对付我的话
So if y'all got ideas about getting rid of me,

06:17.690 --> 06:22.050
