I suggest you make other plans.

07:00.000 --> 07:02.990
那狗日的到处和我们作对
Son of a bitch has got a countermove for everything.

07:03.000 --> 07:05.810
这次不会了
Not for this.

07:07.280 --> 07:10.780
谁会被踢出  我还是你
Odd men out. Me and you.

07:10.790 --> 07:12.620
什么意思?
What do you mean?

07:12.630 --> 07:15.070
看你现在和谁在一起
Look who you're walking with right now.

07:15.080 --> 07:16.730
你本应该和他们步调一致的
You should be up there,

07:16.740 --> 07:19.100
一起安排怎么逃出去
calling the shots with the rest of the suits.

07:19.110 --> 07:22.560
-没错  那又怎么样?   -怎么样...
-Yeah? So?  -So.

07:22.570 --> 07:25.410
斯科菲尔德来这儿只有一个目的
Scofield is only here for one reason.

07:25.420 --> 07:27.060
就是他哥哥
His brother.

07:27.070 --> 07:29.150
他只需要两样东西
And he only needs two things.

07:29.160 --> 07:33.040
老头的钱  还有土匪头子的飞机
The old man's money, and the mob boss's plane.

07:33.050 --> 07:35.250
他根本用不着你
He don't need you.

07:35.260 --> 07:38.740
你只不过是碰巧和他一个牢房而已
You just happened to be in the same cell when he got here.

07:38.750 --> 07:39.920
你和厕所
You and the toilet.

07:39.930 --> 07:41.970
我为此做了很多
I've done a lot of work on this thing.

07:41.980 --> 07:44.380
我又何尝不是呢
Exactly. Me too.

07:44.390 --> 07:47.040
咱们都是给人家当苦力的
We're just the labourers on this thing, man.

07:47.050 --> 07:49.080
真到该逃出去的时候
The night that fish goes into that hole,

07:49.090 --> 07:51.740
你真的认为他会带上这么多累赘么?
you think he wants all that extra baggage?

07:51.750 --> 07:53.760
这就是咱们
Cos that's all we are.

07:53.770 --> 07:57.270
我不管你要怎样  我要走了
I don't know about you, but I'm going.

07:58.900 --> 08:03.120
他到底告诉了你多少呢?
How much does he tell you, anyways?

08:03.130 --> 08:06.400
还是只有他一个人知道?
Or does he keep it all to himself?

08:06.410 --> 08:10.340
他肯定会说  你知道的越少越少  对么?
Yeah, he probably tells you the less you know the better, right?

08:10.350 --> 08:12.190
你根本什么都不知道
You don't know what you're talking about.

08:12.200 --> 08:13.820
他什么都告诉我了
He tells me everything.

08:13.830 --> 08:19.140
他要真都告诉你了  那你就不需要他了
If he tells you everything, then you don't need him.

08:19.150 --> 08:24.220
咱们可以自己逃出去  我和你
Now, we can go by ourselves. Me and you.

08:24.780 --> 08:27.570
或者你可以等
Or, you know, you can wait, and see

08:27.580 --> 08:31.400
然后看看斯科菲尔德到底 愿不愿意带上闲杂人等
if Scofield really wants to carry a heavy weight.

08:31.410 --> 08:34.520
你决定吧  伙计
It's up to you, papi.

08:42.000 --> 08:44.700
嘿  我还等着呢
Yo. I'm still waiting.

08:44.710 --> 08:46.050
在等什么?
What for?

08:46.060 --> 08:48.660
我帮你搞定了那块手表 我的工作呢?
I swiped you that watch, man. Where's my PI?

08:48.670 --> 08:50.090
根本不可能
That's not gonna happen.

08:50.100 --> 08:51.070
你答应过我
You promised.

08:51.080 --> 08:55.290
我说我会考虑  或许在不远的将来
I said I'd think about it. Maybe somewhere down the road.

08:55.300 --> 08:59.180
我才不信你的鬼话呢
Yeah, I ain't gonna hold my breath.

09:07.730 --> 09:09.240
那我该怎么做?
What do you want me to do?

09:09.250 --> 09:10.460
快去找人! 快去!
Get somebody.

09:10.470 --> 09:13.510
不  不  不! 不要  他们看到子弹肯定会报警的
No, no, they see a bullet, they're gonna call the cops.

09:13.520 --> 09:15.450
这不是没办法了么? 我是不会让你死的
We don't have a choice! I'm not gonna let you die.

09:15.460 --> 09:16.920
找到它!
Find it.

09:16.930 --> 09:17.480
什么?
What?

09:17.490 --> 09:19.530
子弹  找到它然后挖出来
The bullet. Just find it and dig it out.

09:19.540 --> 09:22.600
我办不到  -照我说的做!
I can't.  -Do it!

09:49.090 --> 09:51.820
斯科菲尔德呢?
Where's Scofield?

09:55.410 --> 09:57.480
原来在这儿
There you are.

09:57.490 --> 10:01.320
刚去牢房找过你  哪儿都找不到你
Just looked for you in your cell. Couldn't find you anyplace.

10:01.330 --> 10:03.790
当然  也没发现你的信用卡
Couldn't find your credit card either.

10:03.800 --> 10:05.880
