10:14.450 --> 10:19.920
你是怎么把一个嫁给 重罪犯的女孩弄到美国来的呢?
What do you call a girl who married a felon to get into the United States?

10:19.930 --> 10:21.850
她来这里的目的又是什么呢?
Why'd she have to come here, anyway?

10:21.860 --> 10:23.800
