No strip clubs in Whazitstan?

10:23.810 --> 10:25.790
-贝利克警官  -是警长
-Officer Bellick...  -Captain.

10:25.800 --> 10:29.600
好  能否在别的时间进行您的审问呢?
Fine. Do you mind conducting your inquisitions on your own time?

10:29.610 --> 10:31.780
