I don't have to justify myself to you.

12:03.280 --> 12:04.880
不  你必须要证明一下
Oh, you're gonna have to.

12:04.890 --> 12:07.500
否则这把老骨头会拖我们后腿的
Them old bones is gonna be dragging us down.

12:07.510 --> 12:10.630
或许我现在就折断几根试试
Maybe I'll just snap a few right now...

12:10.640 --> 12:12.100
你尽管来
